title: TCL 30 XE 5G coming to T-Mobile and Metro for under $200
content:
TCL might not be the most popular smartphone maker around, but the company has had moderate success in the budget market for a few years now. The TCL 30 XE and TCL 30 V were both revealed earlier this year at CES 2022, and about a month after the TCL 30 V showed up at

The post TCL 30 XE 5G coming to T-Mobile and Metro for under $200 appeared first on xda-developers.
description: One of TCL's newest budget 5G phones, the TCL 30 XE 5G, is coming to T-Mobile and Metro by T-Mobile later this month.
